{
  "id": "20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
  "name": "SpaceKonceptRental - Enquiry Handoff Readiness Template",
  "active": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# READINESS TEMPLATE\n\n- Inactive repo-side skeleton for the SKR quote/enquiry handoff.\n- Import only for review after hosted Supabase migration approval and n8n operator review.\n- Do not activate until the manual HMAC, timestamp freshness, idempotency, and email handoff steps are implemented in n8n.\n\n## Required manual configuration:\n\n- **Receive SKR Enquiry Handoff**\n  - `path`: Replace the placeholder with the reviewed n8n webhook path in n8n only.",
        "height": 460,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000101",
      "name": "Readiness template note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1020,
        -420
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# SECURITY GATES ARE MANUAL\n\n- Static export does not include credential bindings, secret values, webhook IDs, execution data, or real recipient values.\n- Before activation, replace the manual placeholder with n8n-side verification for timestamp freshness and HMAC SHA-256 over `<timestamp>.<raw body>`.\n- Add a durable idempotency check keyed by `x-skr-idempotency-key` before sending any internal handoff.\n- Add the n8n-owned email or notification node with credentials configured in n8n, not in this file.\n\n## Required manual configuration:\n\n- **Manual HMAC And Idempotency Gate**\n  - Replace this placeholder with verified n8n nodes before activation.\n- **Send Internal Handoff Placeholder**\n  - Replace with the reviewed n8n-owned email or notification node before activation.",
        "height": 540,
        "width": 560,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000102",
      "name": "Manual security gate note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -460,
        -500
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "SKR_ENQUIRY_HANDOFF_WEBHOOK_PATH_PLACEHOLDER",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "rawBody": true
        }
      },
